dspace-development.title: Symplectic Elements: Searching queues seem frozen

comments.body: Given a thorough review of the application logs by Symplectic Support, no clear causes for this error could be readily identified without directly accessing the server environments. As this requires a more direct access to the code base for proper diagnosis, I have scheduled a meeting for 04/28/22 from 14:00 - 15:00 EDT for a screen-sharing session with a support specialist. Should this fail to yield any actionable items for our team, this may need to be delayed until the Digital Science team has begun to undertake the migration for the Elements installations.
